snippet.title: Trailer Car Repair Steam
snippet.description:
Game coming to Steam as early as 2025
Add to Wishlist on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2904040?utm_source=YT

Car Repair is a simulation game in which players will test their ingenuity and ethics by making difficult decisions. Will you risk quality for cost savings, or will you strive to maintain a reputation for reliability? From mixing petrol and water to choosing the cheapest parts, every choice has consequences.

Music:
@chiroman6295
